(World, world..)&lt;br /&gt;
Search back time, when you used to sing along&lt;br /&gt;
To the music of your soul&lt;br /&gt;
Song of faith you can change, it&#039;s not too late&lt;br /&gt;
People..stop fighting, angels are crying&lt;br /&gt;
We can be better, love is the answer..&lt;br /&gt;
Search inside, are there anymore tears to cry ?&lt;br /&gt;
Don&#039;t you wonder why ?&lt;br /&gt;
